al shooter where the screen scrolls as you move from left to right. Some parts of the game require you to look behind the hero firing into the screen as aliens come towards from the distance as well as moving in other directions like in a lift. You can also be driving into the screen trying to shoot aliens.","total_rating":79.30117566958613,"total_rating_count":25,"url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/aliens","videos":[{"id":89499,"video_id":"Vs2yN8iVb5s"}],"websites":[{"id":848697,"url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aliens_(1990_video_game)","type":{"id":3,"type":"Wikipedia"}}]}